</emphasis>
Total length 
<quantity box="[591,701,1152,1179]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.17" pageId="12" pageNumber="161" unit="mm" value="4.17">4.17 mm</quantity>
. 
<emphasis box="[713,813,1153,1179]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="161">Carapace</emphasis>
: Length 
<quantity box="[919,1028,1152,1179]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.75" pageId="12" pageNumber="161" unit="mm" value="1.75">1.75 mm</quantity>
, width 
<quantity box="[140,252,1188,1214]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.08" pageId="12" pageNumber="161" unit="mm" value="1.08">1.08 mm</quantity>
. Dark charcoal grey with a paler yellowish median stripe extending from behind eyes, wide anteriorly and abruptly narrowing posteriorly. With black striae ra-
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3817246" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3817246" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3817246/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="161" startId="12.[140,222,1622,1644]" targetBox="[155,1073,1280,1602]" targetPageId="12">
